Package net.unicon.cas.addons.info.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCasServiceAccessEvent
    Base Spring ApplicationEvent representing a service access action executed within running CAS server.
    AbstractCasSsoEvent
    Base Spring ApplicationEvent representing a abstract single sign on action executed within running CAS server.
    CasServiceTicketGrantedEvent
    Concrete subclass of AbstractCasServiceAccessEvent representing granting of a service ticket by a CAS server.
    CasServiceTicketValidatedEvent
    Concrete subclass of AbstractCasServiceAccessEvent representing validation of a service ticket by a CAS server.
    CasSsoSessionDestroyedEvent
    Concrete subclass of AbstractCasSsoEvent representing single sign on session destruction event e.g.
    CasSsoSessionEstablishedEvent
    Concrete subclass of AbstractCasSsoEvent representing single sign on session establishment event e.g.
    CentralAuthenticationServiceEventsPublishingAspect
    Aspect implementing a mechanism by which to intercept core CAS runtime events and publish them as Spring ApplicationEvents to ApplicationContext in which CAS server is deployed for further consumption by any number of registered ApplicationListeners.
